author: AC NEWS SERVICE
title: AC hosting conference fall tournament
text:
Angelina baseball AC PRESS PHOTO 
Former Hudson Hornet and current Angelina College Roadrunner Anthony Doss and his AC teammates will host the Region XIV Fall Tournament beginning on Friday and running through Sunday at Roadrunner Field in Lufkin. The schedule includes four games each day. Posted: Wednesday, September 30, 2015 12:30 am AC hosting conference fall tournament AC NEWS SERVICE The Lufkin News
